| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0830 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 63a292d6-168c-5cbd-94bd-55ae0bcba3b8"
